OL,3,CPensioner left 'shaken' after scooter
OL,4,Cstolen ` used to visit wife in care
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FA 90 year old man from Banbury has
OL,8,Fdescribed the "shock of his life"
OL,9,Fafter discovering his mobility scooter
OL,10,Fhad been stolen while he was out
OL,11,Fshopping.
OL,13,FTony Brayne, who has a neurological
OL,14,Fcondition that affects his legs,
OL,15,Frelies on the scooter to visit his
OL,16,Fwife in a care home, to collect
OL,17,Fprescriptions and get to medical
OL,18,Fappointments.
