OL,3,CPensioner left 'shaken' after scooter
OL,4,Cstolen ` used to visit wife in care
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FHe had parked it outside a shop in the
OL,8,Ftown centre last week, leaving the
OL,9,Fkeys in the ignition, but when he came
OL,10,Fback outside, it was gone.
OL,12,F"I just went cold all over," Tony
OL,13,Fsaid. "I just stood there. I could not
OL,14,Fbelieve it was gone."
OL,16,FAn elderly couple parked nearby told
OL,17,Fhim they saw three young men take the
OL,18,Fscooter and drive off down the High
OL,19,FStreet. They helped Tony contact the
OL,20,Fpolice and gave him a lift home.
