OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FTony said the theft has left him
OL,8,Fdeeply upset. "I just cannot imagine
OL,9,Fanybody, even for fun, doing what they
OL,10,Fdid. It's despicable," he said.
OL,12,F"They didn't think about the problems
OL,13,Fthey were causing. At my age, I could
OL,14,Fhave had a stroke or a heart attack."
