OL,3,CPensioner left 'shaken' after scooter
OL,4,Cstolen ` used to visit wife in care
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FHis wife's care home has loaned him a
OL,8,Fscooter so he can continue visiting
OL,9,Fher, but he fears that arrangement
OL,10,Fwon't last long. "Half my life savings
OL,11,Fhave already gone on her care," he
OL,12,Fsaid. "I daren't spend more money in
OL,13,Fcase I run out."
OL,15,FA fundraising page set up by his
OL,16,Fneighbour has since raised more than
OL,17,F#600 to help him buy a replacement.
OL,19,FThames Valley Police are appealing for
OL,20,Fwitnesses or anyone with information
OL,21,Fabout the theft to come forward.
